       byte >00

* Stage (0-23, but starts with 1 during play)
stage:                                 ; >7200
       byte >00

* Wave
wave:                                  ; >7201
       byte >00

* Enemies destroyed not chance stage
enemies_hit:                           ; >7202
       byte >00

* Stage data index
*
* Index (0-7) into #R$8541 (blocks of 8 bytes)
